      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a perfect balance of reliability and pride of ownership. Finished in a timeless metallic coat, the exterior retains a deep gloss, showing only minor stone chips consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, though light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster reflects its history of being enjoyed. Mechanically, it is in top form; the engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and all electronic features\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014function exactly as intended. Recently serviced with a fresh oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection, this car is turn-key ready for its next owner. It has been garage-kept and smoke-free, offering a clean, well-preserved cabin environment that still feels fresh.",
