    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for this reliable ride. It's been such a solid car for me and is still in great shape for its next owner! It runs super smoothly, looks lovely inside and out, and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. If you're looking for something dependable that still has plenty of life left to give, this is the one! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have!",
