    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Key preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise turn-in and camber control expected of the marque. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression and rod bearing clearances\u2014remain within optimal operating parameters. This is a driver-focused specimen optimized for performance and longevity.",
